# Google OAuth 2.0 "Web application" client ID, used for Drive sync.
# Create one at https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# This value is NOT secret — OAuth client IDs are public and embedded in the built site.
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your ID for local dev; set the same
# variable in the Cloudflare Pages project settings for production.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
